{{Top|canon=Dis-remembering}}
'''Disremembering''' was the ultimate insult in [[Bosph (species)|Bosph]] society. Disremembering consisted in ignoring people who had done harmful deeds toward one and not remembering the deed itself either. Many Bosph would disremember the destruction of [[Bosph/Legends|Bosph]] by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Empire]] and go about their businesses without any regard to the Empire at all.

